<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Asrab qolding bogʻimni</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Umrim sensiz sahrodir,
 Nafasim ham roʻyodir,
 Kuylagayman madhingni
 Orzularim dunyodir

[V2]
 Kelding sen hayotimga
 Sevgi ila limmo-lim
 Senla topdim huzurni
 Qiynardi shayton zolim.

[V3]
 Marhamatli Xudosan.
 Kechirding gunohimni
 Shu bilan asrab qolding.
 Yurakdagi bogʻimni!!!</lyrics>
<aka>Umrim Sensiz sahrodir</aka>
</song>